name: doppyo
raw_meta_yaml:
{% set version = "0.0.2" %}

package:
  name: doppyo
  version: {{ version }}

source:
  url: https://pypi.io/packages/source/d/doppyo/doppyo-{{ version }}.tar.gz
  sha256: 902f0825274aded70e837d51e1b47f09f6cefc0b0b4e6893680a3e7200c746a0

build:
  number: 1
  noarch: python
  script: "{{ PYTHON }} -m pip install . --no-deps -vv"

requirements:
  host:
    - python >=3
    - pip
  run:
    - python >=3
    - bokeh >=0.12.13
    - bottleneck >=1.2.1
    - cartopy >=0.16.0
    - dask >=0.17.1
    - matplotlib-base >=2.2.2
    - netcdf4 >=1.3.1
    - numpy >=1.13.3
    - pandas >=0.22.0
    - pyspharm >=1.0.9
    - pytest >=3.5.0
    - scipy >=1.0.0
    - windspharm >=1.6.0
    - xarray >=0.10.7

test:
  imports:
    - doppyo

about:
  home: https://github.com/csiro-dcfp/doppyo
  license: MIT
  license_family: MIT
  license_file: LICENSE
  summary: "Diagnostics and verification tools for climate forecasts"

extra:
  recipe-maintainers:
    - jmunroe
    - dougiesquire
